  "notes": "Mt. Mortar 1F Inside (20x27 blocks, 40x54 tiles, confirmed: MountMortar1FInside.blk = 540 bytes). The main interior cave floor — the largest of the four Mt. Mortar areas. Connects back to 1F Outside via four exits, has one passage up to 2F Inside and one down to B1F. A Strength boulder at (21,43) must be pushed aside to reach the southern exits. Two trainers: Pokemaniac Miller (Nidoking Lv17 + Nidoqueen Lv17) near the south-east and Super Nerd Markus (Slowpoke Lv19 with Strength) in the center. Markus is one of two paired Super Nerds exploring Mt. Mortar — his partner Hugh is on 2F. 8 items: Escape Rope, Max Revive, Hyper Potion, Max Potion, Nugget, Iron, Ultra Ball (all visible pokeballs) and hidden Max Repel. Tileset: TILESET_DARK_CAVE. Music: MUSIC_UNION_CAVE."
